Class Shape

  • java.lang.Object
    • Shape
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Drawable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Oval, Polygon, Sinusoid

    public abstract class Shape
extends java.lang.Object
implements Drawable
    This class holds the location and color of the shape, as well as whether the shape is filled.
